query:
SELECT r.id, r.request_number, r.current_stage, m.name as mosque_name, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quotations q WHERE q.request_id = r.id) as quotation_count
FROM service_requests r 
LEFT JOIN mosques m ON r.mosque_id = m.id
ORDER BY quotation_count DESC
LIMIT 5;
